Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember the recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If only there was somewhere I could find that information!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And now there is! It's called... book!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say book?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How convenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel suffocated by the weight of my past mistakes and the hurt I've caused my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If only there was a way to atone for what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone say "book"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,– No! I said-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yes you did, you said book, we all heard. You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cured!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in conclusion, read a book!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no matter the problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,books fix everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- I love books, but I wouldn't say they fix everythi-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- EVERYTHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to know?
