Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be best friends and do everything together and be the coolest guys ever-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm not really looking for commitment right now, I'm kinda just focusing on my career.
