Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you challenging me, button?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, I accept your shiny red challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Check and mate, button.
