Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use this mysterious red button as a weapon to finally defeat that nosy Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to is... whoops!
