Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A mysterious red button that we don't know what it does or anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,LET'S PUSH IT!
